name: Olivia Casta
description:
Olivia Claudia Motta Casta, an Instagram model known to be fake, the owner uses CGI on herself. In real she is a middle aged women who looks completely different.

But anyway, I like her doll face, so it was nice to do a TI with her.

I was surprised that there is no TI with her on the site, only LORA.

I hope someone likes this TI. As always, I will be happy to receive a review or feedback
